  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5977132">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5977132/" class="title-link">乡镇经历很真实</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5977132"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2002383/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2002383/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">haha</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-05-20"
      class="main-meta">2013-05-20 20:42:12</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5977132_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  很不错的一本书，对官场内微妙关系的刻画很精彩，尤其是开篇对侯卫东乡镇经历的描写，很真实。正因为其真实，所以很能引起有相似经历的人们的共鸣。虽然有些情节一看就知道是虚构的，但是为了那些真实的有感而发我宁愿忽略掉这微小的瑕疵。情节引人入胜，发人深省。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
